---
title: Evelina
desc: Case study for Evelina. An all-natural essential-oil aromatherapy scent melts and ceramic wamers inspired by nature.
---
extends layouts/_layout
block content
	+header('', 'header__burger_dark')
	.product.evelina
		.product__head
			.product__center.center
				.product__wrap
					.product__stage.stage(data-aos="animation-scale-y") Design & Development
					h1.product__title.title.h1(data-aos="animation-scale-y" data-aos-delay="150") Evelina
					.product__info.h5(data-aos="animation-scale-y" data-aos-delay="300") An all-natural essential-oil aromatherapy scent melts and ceramic wamers inspired by nature.
			.embelish__1
				img.js-parallax(data-scale="1.25" data-delay=".01" data-orientation="up" src="img/shapes/l-orange-blob-1.svg" alt="")
		.product__bg(style="background-image: url('img/case-evelina-screens.png')")
		.product__body
			.product__center.center
				.product__row
					.product__overview.h4(data-aos="animation-scale-y") Overview
					.product__content.content(data-aos="animation-scale-y" data-aos-delay="200")
						p Design a relaxing and unique e-shopping experience through Shopify.
						p The goal of the website was to convert their etsy store into a shopify website. The design creates a zen shopping experience without overpowering the design of the products. The website is built on Shopifyâ€™s platform with dynamic sections and custom elements. The website is fully responsive and 100% optimized for speed and usability.
				.product__preview
					.img__container
						img.product__pic.js-parallax(data-scale="1.25" data-delay=".01" data-orientation="up" src="img/case-evelina-home.png" alt="")
					
			.desc
				.embelish__2
					img.js-parallax(data-scale="2" data-delay=".01" data-orientation="down" src="img/shapes/l-orange-blob-2.svg" alt="")
				.desc__center.center
					.desc__list
						+descPreview('img/case-evelina-1.png', '')
						+descPreview('img/case-evelina-2.png', '200')
						+descPreview('img/case-evelina-3.png', '')
						+descPreview('img/case-evelina-4.png', '200')
					+descButtons('/hamsapay', '/lift')
	+footerTiny